Ruby/GStreamer
==============

Ruby/GStreamer is a Ruby binding for GStreamer.

Requirements
------------

    Ruby:       http://www.ruby-lang.org/
    GStreamer:  http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/

Install
-------

    0. install Ruby (>= 1.9.x) and GStreamer (>= 0.10.x).
    1. ruby extconf.rb
    2. make
    3. su
    4. make install

